snippet.title: TenZ Ranks VALORANT Pros (Ft. Boaster)
snippet.description:
TenZ ranks VALORANT pros from across the VCT, breaking down how players from Fnatic, NRG, G2, Sentinels, and ZETA Division stack up in his tier list. Later in the video, Boaster joins to share his own takes and help finalize the rankings. Who do you think deserves S Tier?
